@startuml SD08_ChatRealtime
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #EBF5FB
    BorderColor #2980B9
    FontColor #1A252F
    FontSize 12
}
skinparam actor {
    BackgroundColor #D5E8D4
    BorderColor #27AE60
    FontColor #1A252F
}
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #2C3E50
    LifeLineBorderColor #AEB6BF
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #F2F3F4
    GroupBorderColor #2980B9
    GroupBackgroundColor #EBF5FB
    GroupFontColor #1A5276
    DividerBackgroundColor #EAECEE
    DividerBorderColor #AEB6BF
}

title <size:16><b>SD08 - Chat Real-time (Socket.io)</b></size>\n<color:#5D6D7E><size:12>UC08 + UC13 | CellphoneK</size></color>

actor "Khách Hàng" as Customer
participant "ChatScreen\n(Customer)" as ChatScreen
participant "Socket.io\nClient" as SocketClient
participant "Server.js\n(Socket.io Server)" as SocketServer
participant "ChatController" as ChatCtrl
participant "AdminChatDetail\nScreen" as AdminChatScreen
participant "Socket.io\nClient (Admin)" as SocketAdmin
actor "Quản Trị Viên\n(Admin)" as Admin
participant "Database\n(MySQL)" as DB

== Bước 1: Khởi Tạo Kết Nối ==

Customer -> ChatScreen : Mở màn hình Chat
ChatScreen -> ChatCtrl : GET /support-info\n(Bearer token)
ChatCtrl -> DB : User.findOne({role: 'admin'})
DB --> ChatCtrl : adminInfo
ChatCtrl --> ChatScreen : {id, username, name, avatar}

ChatScreen -> ChatCtrl : GET /chat/history/:adminId\n(Bearer token)
ChatCtrl -> DB : ChatMessage.findAll(\nsenderId=user OR receiverId=user)
DB --> ChatCtrl : messages
ChatCtrl --> ChatScreen : Lịch sử tin nhắn

ChatScreen -> SocketClient : socket.connect(serverURL)
SocketClient -> SocketServer : io.connect + emit('join', userId)
SocketServer --> SocketClient : Xác nhận kết nối

== Bước 2: Khách Hàng Gửi Tin Nhắn ==

Customer -> ChatScreen : Nhập và gửi tin nhắn
ChatScreen -> SocketClient : socket.emit('send_message',\n{senderId, receiverId: adminId, content})
SocketClient -> SocketServer : Event 'send_message'

SocketServer -> DB : ChatMessage.create(\n{senderId, receiverId,\ncontent, isRead: false})
DB --> SocketServer : savedMessage

SocketServer -> SocketAdmin : socket.to(adminRoom).emit(\n'receive_message', message)
SocketAdmin -> AdminChatScreen : Nhận tin nhắn mới real-time
AdminChatScreen --> Admin : Hiển thị tin nhắn mới\n+ badge thông báo

== Bước 3: Admin Trả Lời ==

Admin -> AdminChatScreen : Nhập và gửi phản hồi
AdminChatScreen -> SocketAdmin : socket.emit('send_message',\n{senderId: adminId,\nreceiverId: customerId, content})
SocketAdmin -> SocketServer : Event 'send_message'

SocketServer -> DB : ChatMessage.create(\n{senderId: adminId,\nreceiverId: customerId,\ncontent, isRead: false})
DB --> SocketServer : savedMessage

SocketServer -> SocketClient : socket.to(customerRoom).emit(\n'receive_message', message)
SocketClient -> ChatScreen : Nhận phản hồi real-time
ChatScreen --> Customer : Hiển thị tin nhắn\ncủa Admin

== Bước 4: Đánh Dấu Đã Đọc ==

note over ChatScreen, DB
    Khi người dùng mở lịch sử chat,
    GET /chat/history/:targetId sẽ tự động
    đánh dấu isRead = true cho các tin nhắn
    mà người dùng là receiverId
end note

@enduml
